        "meta_description": "Sean Penn briefly opened up about the journey he and Robin Wright took from estranged divorcees to friends again in the years since their 2010 divorce. “It turns out it’s a lot quicker to repair a friendship after divorce if there are not kids involved,” he told The New York Times. “It took Robin and I quite a while.\"",
